flowchart TD

%% ========== 用户输入 ==========
A[User Input CLI] --> B[Load Context<br/>Session Memory<br/>Long-term Memory]

%% ========== 上下文加载 ==========
B --> B3[Intent Hints Generation]

B3 --> C

%% ========== Orchestrator ==========
C[Orchestrator Decision Loop]

%% ========== 决策分支 ==========
C -->|action: rag| D[RAG Agent]
C -->|action: tool| E[Tool Agent]
C -->|action: memory| F[Memory Agent]
C -->|action: answer| G[Generate Final Response]
C -->|action: clarify| H[Ask Clarification]

%% ========== RAG ==========
D --> D1[Vector Search ChromaDB]
D --> D2[BM25 Search]
D1 --> D3[Merge + RRF]
D2 --> D3
D3 --> D4[Reranker BGE]
D4 --> D5[Filtered Context]
D5 --> C

%% ========== Tool ==========
E --> E1[Tool Registry]
E1 --> E2[Tool Execution / MCP]
E2 --> E3[Formatted Result]
E3 --> C

%% ========== Memory ==========
F --> F1[Session Memory Read]
F --> F2[mem0 Search]
F1 --> F3[Memory Context]
F2 --> F3
F3 --> C

%% ========== 生成回复 ==========
G --> I[Context Assembly]
I --> J[LLM Response]
J --> K[Post Processing]

%% ========== 澄清 ==========
H --> K

%% ========== 后处理 ==========
K --> K1[Update Session Memory]
K --> K2[Write Long-term Memory]
K --> L[Return to User]
